OL,3,CThe 'forever chemical' PFAS: Your
OL,4,Cquestions answered
OL,6,FIt has been revealed four pesticides
OL,7,Fused in Jersey contain the chemical
OL,8,FPFAS.
OL,10,FThey are among 25 PFAS-containing
OL,11,Fpesticides that campaigners in the UK
OL,12,Fare calling to be banned after they
OL,13,Fsay the chemicals are 'toxic' to
OL,14,Fhumans and insects.
OL,16,FMike Renouard from the Jersey Farmers'
OL,17,FUnion says: "I wasn't aware of this
OL,18,Funtil recently, we are trying to phase
OL,19,Fout these products as quickly as we
OL,20,Fcan.
