OL,3,CThe 'forever chemical' PFAS: Your
OL,4,Cquestions answered
OL,6,FIt was concluded in 2022 that there
OL,7,Fwere 'higher than expected' levels of
OL,8,FPFAS in the blood samples of islanders
OL,9,Fliving in Jersey following Government-
OL,10,Fbacked testing of 72 people from 31
OL,11,Faddresses very close to Jersey Airport.
OL,13,FThe 'forever chemical' leaked into
OL,14,Fprivate borehole water supplies after
OL,15,Fit was used in firefighting foams
OL,16,Fduring a training day at Jersey
OL,17,FAirport in 1991.
