OL,3,CThe 'forever chemical' PFAS: Your
OL,4,Cquestions answered
OL,6,FHowever, the PFAS levels are
OL,7,Fconsidered to be at a safe limit today
OL,8,Fand there is not thought to be wider
OL,9,Fconcern.
OL,11,FSome residents in Jersey claim it has
OL,12,Faffected their health and have set up
OL,13,Fa petition to 'clean Jersey's water,
OL,14,Fbuild a treatment plant and improve
OL,15,FPFAS related healthcare'.
