OL,3,CThe 'forever chemical' PFAS: Your
OL,4,Cquestions answered
OL,6,FHigh levels of PFAS have been linked
OL,7,Fto cancer, bowel disease and birth
OL,8,Fdefects - however, in 2022 Jersey's
OL,9,FDirector of Public Health, Deputy
OL,10,FKaren Wilson, insisted more research
OL,11,Fis needed to establish exactly how
OL,12,FPFAS affects the body.
