OL,3,CThe 'forever chemical' PFAS: Your
OL,4,Cquestions answered
OL,6,FOn Thursday 30 January, Jersey's
OL,7,Fscientific panel on perfluoroalkyl and
OL,8,Fpolyfluoroalkyl substances (PFAS)
OL,9,Frevealed it was considering
OL,10,Frecommending a type of cholesterol
OL,11,Fmedication to those living in the west
OL,12,Fof the island who have a high
OL,13,Fconcentration of the chemical in their
OL,14,Fblood.
OL,16,FThe panel are discussing a series of
OL,17,Foptions which they will finalise and
OL,18,Fthen give to the Government who will
OL,19,Fultimately decide what to do.
