OL,3,CThe 'forever chemical' PFAS: Your
OL,4,Cquestions answered
OL,6,FAt this stage, medication is only a
OL,7,Fdraft recommendation which will be
OL,8,Fdiscussed further by the panel and put
OL,9,Fto islanders to give their thoughts
OL,10,Ftoo.
OL,12,FJersey Water, which supplies the water
OL,13,Ffor the island, says it monitors the
OL,14,Flevel of PFAS at the treatment works
OL,15,Fand in the affected water sources
OL,16,Fthrough an extensive sampling and
OL,17,Fanalysis programme across the year.
