OL,3,CThe 'forever chemical' PFAS: Your
OL,4,Cquestions answered
OL,6,FIn spring, one of the four pesticides
OL,7,Fincluding PFAS in Jersey is used on
OL,8,Fthe leaf of the crop of royal potatoes.
OL,10,FFarmers say it is used to keep a
OL,11,Ffungal disease under control and claim
OL,12,Fwithout it, the whole crop would be in
OL,13,Fjeopardy.
OL,15,FHowever, they add this is only once or
OL,16,Ftwice a year, it is not an active
OL,17,Fingredient and the amount is minimal.
